column2: select top #  p.specObjID, p.z, s.zErr, T.SFR, p.minSFR, p.maxSFR, p.logMass, p.minLogMass,  from  stellarMassPassivePort p JOIN emissionLinesPort t ON t.specObjID = p.specObjID JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranWideNoDust s ON s.specObjID = t.specObjID  WHERE  p.z BETWEEN # AND # AND p.SFR >#
